<p class="p">The energy substitution effect was taken to be the substitution of logging residue, processing residue, and waste wood for heavy oil in energy generation, and the relevant annual reduction in the volume of carbon emissions was estimated using Eq. (
 <xref rid="Equ22" ref-type="" class="xref">22</xref>).
